00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:21.080
And this in contrast
to sometimes

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:23.260
what gets done in a
wheelchair space for example,

00:19:23.260 --> 00:19:28.909
is to send a kind of
rickety hospital wheelchair

00:19:28.909 --> 00:19:29.950
over to that environment.

00:19:29.950 --> 00:19:32.730
Where it lasts, like a lot of
