00:27:21.890 --> 00:27:24.960
And then secondly,
there's activation energy

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:28.170
to any kind of a
collaborative effort, which

00:27:28.170 --> 00:27:32.464
if you don't cross you have
a lot of difficulty making

00:27:32.464 --> 00:27:33.130
anything happen.

